step_data.thought: The user wants to view all items in their wish list. The current page already shows 1 item, and the 'Show' dropdown is set to 10 items per page. Since only 1 item is shown, it is likely that the 'Show' dropdown is set to a page size that is too small to display all items. Changing the dropdown to 50 or 100 items per page might show more items. I will select the '50' option from the 'Show' dropdown to see if it displays more items in the wish list.
